description:
This is a 45 minute workout called 'Guided Meditation for Calm (Anxiety / OCD / Depression / Pain) Spoken by Michael Sealey' from the channel Michael Sealey.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: If you're in need of some healing serenity, or you would simply like a soothing, relaxing time out to calm yourself down, I have created this guided meditation for calm, just for you. This spoken meditation encourages a relaxing awareness of the breath, and also a gentle detachment from any effects of anxiety, OCD, depression, or pain. This meditation session is also useful for alleviating symptoms of rumination, or overthinking, and for relaxing the mind and body into your very best of nightly, calm and deep sleep.
